reviewText: My kids, who are now 22 and 28, absolutely absolutely loved the Kidsongs videos.  I now have an infant grandson so wanted to make sure that he saw some of the oldie but goldie's that they had to offer.  He absolutely loves watching them.
My son collects these, which are often hard to find.  This arrived in good condition and on time.  He is enjoying it.

This DVD was delivered on time in excellent condition. I was skeptical at first about buying used DVDs, but all my experiences (4 different ones) so far have been great. My special needs sons loves the Kidsongs series especially this one. I suspect I will be buying more in the future.
